{"tid":1224534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次運動學到d咩","createTime":"2019-06-15T03:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:37:31.000Z","uid":107362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"23e2aa64c6207b0a4dbc86087a4bad8ce742b796","tid":1224534,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">繼續抗爭 撤回修例</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1- 睇急症唔使話自己去過邊度（外遊除外），因為醫管局系統有後門<br />\n<br />\n2- 隨時準備camera 因為警察依家連記者都打<br />\n<br />\n3- 邊一方使用暴力 邊一方就會失去支持<br />\n<br />\n4- 香港係經濟城市 做唔做到生意大過係咪普選特首<br />\n<br />\n5- 一百萬人既遊行可能即時爭取唔到d咩 但呢個係抗爭運動既起點 新聞價值之所在<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講"},{"pid":"d16af772f6993f367091fd4c13c831b73cd43d7d","tid":1224534,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"下一個目標？真普選？"},{"pid":"cf523ee7834ba3d76e0b70388bfbcb5d576da835","tid":1224534,"uid":1303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻少少時間，希望可以入黎睇睇！<br />\n<br />\n抗爭之後，有更重要既事我地要去做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223305\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223305</a><br />\n<br />\n總有一日，朗朗乾坤，一片清明！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979fe257a7b7cf26af068c027ca976a3ea406984","tid":1224534,"uid":1303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d16af772f6993f367091fd4c13c831b73cd43d7d","tid":1224534,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"下一個目標？真普選？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:53:13.000Z","msg":"請支持限左權先！<br />\n否則一世比狗暴力鎮壓！"},{"pid":"2cdad217c994a46141f28d9402446bee8c73af15","tid":1224534,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"